rhood may jointly be shaped by its most massive satellites. As such,\nthe current structure of the MW suggests we are seeing the process of disc\nheating by satellite interactions in action.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2016 20:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
