simple evolution models. After\nthe cycle of matter in and out of dust reaches a steady state, the dust growth\nbalances the destruction operating on similar timescales of 350 Myr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2016 21:03:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-09"}
