rization relation in general. Remarkably enough, we find that\nfor some particular interesting cases, like two-qubit pure states or the\nentanglement concentration protocol, both proposals are coincident.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2016 00:48:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2017 13:17:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-12"}
